ying glass on top of financial market info\" data-id=\"186805810\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3872px\" height=\"2592px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SusanneB</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article is part of a series that provides an ongoing analysis of the changes made to David Tepper\u2019s 13F portfolio on a quarterly basis. It is based on Appaloosa Management\u2019s regulatory <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1656456/000165645624000004/0001656456-24-000004-index.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">13F Form</a> filed on 11/14/2024. Please visit</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/186805810/image_186805810.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743746-tracking-david-teppers-appaloosa-management-portfolio-q3-2024-update", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 08:30:00"}, {"id": "4743753", "title": "XCCC: An Overlooked High-Yielder With Compelling Risk-Adjusted Attributes", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255522240/image_1255522240.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bonds the word on wooden cubes, cubes stand on a reflective surface, in the background is a business diagram.\" data-id=\"1255522240\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5906px\" height=\"3543px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255522240/image_1255522240.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255522240/image_1255522240.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255522240/image_1255522240.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255522240/image_1255522240.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255522240/image_1255522240.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255522240/image_1255522240.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255522240/image_1255522240.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255522240/image_1255522240.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Dzmitry Skazau</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>High yield bonds are in focus today as we take a look at the <strong>BondBloxx CCC Rated USD High Yield Corporate Bond ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XCCC\" title=\"BondBloxx CCC Rated USD High Yield Corporate Bond ETF\">XCCC</a></span>).</strong></p> <p>The XCCC ETF remains relatively under-covered. However, its recent performance warrants coverage. As displayed below, the vehicle has</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1255522240/image_1255522240.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743753-xccc-etf-an-overlooked-high-yielder-with-compelling-risk-adjusted-attributes", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 08:17:04"}, {"id": "4743751", "title": "S&P 500 2025 Prediction: Global Contagion Threatens Wall Street", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1254837834/image_1254837834.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Global Spreading\" data-id=\"1254837834\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6160px\" height=\"3465px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1254837834/image_1254837834.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1254837834/image_1254837834.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1254837834/image_1254837834.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1254837834/image_1254837834.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1254837834/image_1254837834.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1254837834/image_1254837834.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1254837834/image_1254837834.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1254837834/image_1254837834.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">imaginima</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Intro</h2> <p>Regarding 2024 there were many doubts since the Sahm Rule and the inversion of the yield curve indicated that there would be a recession soon. These indicators have been flawless to date, but in financial markets nothing is certain, and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1254837834/image_1254837834.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743751-sp-500-2025-prediction-global-contagion-threatens-wall-street", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 08:15:08"}, {"id": "4743748", "title": "Google's Waymo Continues To Surge Ahead Of Tesla", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Waymo Jaguar driverless car drives on urban street in San Francisco\" data-id=\"2158937921\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158937921/image_2158937921.jpg